      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6706cceec2a37.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6706cceece2bd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6706cceed6b83.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6706cceed3490.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6706cceed7a67.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6706cceed72b4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6706ccef0cb36.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; twanswated the wentire game!&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: the entire game is now (mostly) translated to uwu language!&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Now has NPC dialog and other text translated!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Replaces all of the game's english text to be cuter and more uwu-like (I honestly don't know how to describe it)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;It was made using a python script that replaces all "l" and "r" letters with "w".&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;There are two versions of this mod: uwulang and uwulang-overkill.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The overkill version also adds w before every vowel, which is... overkill.&lt;br&gt;(I would not recommend using it)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Examples: &lt;br&gt;Tree Branch - twee bwanch&lt;br&gt;Hylian Shroom - hywian shwoom&lt;br&gt;Balloon - bawwoon&lt;br&gt;Master Sword - mastew swowd&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Uses custom rstbl files&lt;br&gt;Files edited: &lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;EUen.Product.110.sarc.zs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;USen.Product.110.sarc.zs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;Tested working in version 1.1.1 with Yuzu and on my hacked switch&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Why did I make this? I honestly don't know&lt;br&gt;</description>
