    <item>
      <title>Beta Champion's Tunic [PORT]</title>
      <author>hulmerist</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/545876</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/545876#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">a7613e1682d0330b96fe07d02e20ace559ad9e92</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 21:12:50 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66fc744a11da2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66fc7458daef1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66fc7458ea0cc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66fc74771743f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66fc7476bfb40.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66fc74770416f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66fc74ac12c62.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66fc80b2ae0a9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67059e3c5beb6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Beta Champion's Tunic V3&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1700231"&gt;Sonic Gamer&lt;/a&gt; has updated the original mod and overhauled the textures for the tunic, so I've gone ahead and ported over V3 of the Beta Champion's Tunic. See screenshots for the changes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Overhauled the beta tunic to better resemble the E3 &amp; Game Awards 2014 footage.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a TOTK port of the &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/531768"&gt;Beta + Royal Guard Champion's Tunics&lt;/a&gt; mod from BOTW, originally created by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1700231"&gt;Sonic Gamer&lt;/a&gt;. I got permission from the original creator to port this mod over to TOTK as well as upload it to GameBanana. Importantly, this port is &lt;b&gt;only&lt;/b&gt; of the beta tunic texture from that mod.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod edits the Tunic of Memories to more closely resemble the Champion's Tunic seen in the &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XZmxvig1dXE"&gt;E3 2014 Trailer&lt;/a&gt;. As you can see, the chest symbol design is different than the vanilla version. Apart from that, the rest of the design remains the same. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Pictured in the screenshots are the &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/510969" class="SelectedElement"&gt;Dark Right Arm&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/447252"&gt;Fair Skinned Link&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/447788"&gt;Links Natural Hair Colours&lt;/a&gt; mods.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;All credit goes to &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1700231"&gt;Sonic Gamer&lt;/a&gt; for the design and texture. I simply ported the mod.</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/beta_champion_s_tunic_totk_v3.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/beta_champion_s_tunic_totk_v2.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/beta_champion_s_tunic_totk.zip" type="application/zip"/>
