      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 21:21:08 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67039273bedc7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67039273ee2a7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67039273ce4db.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670392738c24f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67039273ebb2e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67039273f04ce.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67044fe0ea63a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67044fe08975a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Champion's Leathers Chest Armor&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Added an optional version with the chest armor from the Champion's Leathers instead of the Hylian Tunic&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;This mod adds some basic armor to the Tunic of Memories.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Isn't it a bit strange that the tunic which Link wore throughout most of Breath of the Wild has practically no defensive capability? Aside from a single gauntlet on his right arm, the Tunic of Memories is pretty much just a shirt. No wonder it got completely destroyed during the Calamity.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod aims to fix that by giving the Tunic of Memories some extra armor. The Tunic of Memories now has new bracers and chest armor to go along with its gauntlet. Now, it looks more like an outfit fit for adventuring rather than ceremonial garb.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod uses models and textures from the Hylian Tunic, so any mod that recolors the chest armor or bracers of the Hylian Tunic will also affect this mod. This also means that this mod is compatible with any mods that recolor or retexture the Tunic of Memories (&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/451274"&gt;Green Tunic of Memories&lt;/a&gt; shown in the screenshots as an example) since the textures for the armor are independent from the actual tunic.</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/armored_tunic_of_memories.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/champion_s_leathers_armored_tunic_of_memories.zip" type="application/zip"/>
