      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66f039188dfbc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66f03a30b9849.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66f03bd55d988.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66f03be0460ae.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66f03be5e73c1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66f03beb48141.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66f03c10ea2a6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Bug fixes&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed "Secret enemy" spawning in front of the Yiga Hideout&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed a typo in Sooga's description.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;i&gt;"After the cataclysm, Sooga mystireously got spotted near Lookout Landing.&lt;br&gt;Now he is suspected to live in the Yiga Clan Hideout again. Go to the Hideout and defeat him and his&lt;br&gt;well-trained Blademaster-Lieutenants."&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-Purah&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Sooga's Revenge is a mod, wich aims  to make the Yiga Clan Hideout more challenging and&lt;br&gt;interesting. &lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Features&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Enemies&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;New Sooga boss&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;New Yiga Lieutenants&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;A secret enemy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;Weapons&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Windcleaver&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sword of Devotion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Demon Carver Can be found in the Yiga Clan Hideout and in the Hands of someone else...&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;Misc&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Custom Sooga music&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Yiga Weapon Obtain Methods&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Windcleaver&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;-Can be bought in the Yiga Clan Hideout&lt;br&gt;-Dropped by Yiga Lieutenants&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Sword of Devotion&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;-Only obtainable by defeating Sooga&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Demon Carver &lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;-Spawns near the Hideout main gate, leaning at a Stoneheap.&lt;br&gt;- Dropped by &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;a secret enemy&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Current supported languages&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-English&lt;br&gt;-German&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Issues&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hinox boss bar and Bgm needed to be removed to make the Sooga theme work&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Future plans&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Bring back the vicious sickle and equip them to Yiga Footsoldiers&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Credits&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-The Relicts of the Past team for the Yiga-Leutenant texture&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;And that's it. Have fun with the mod</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/soogasrevenge_dbfe8.zip" type="application/zip"/>
